Setup:
- Once per system: ./install.sh
- Once per sesion: source ./activate.sh

Build:
- idf.py set-target esp32 (esp32, esp32s3, or esp32c3)
- idf.py build

Setup environment for nvim:
- ln -s build/compile_commands.json .

Add user to dialout:
- If the group does not exist: sudo groupadd dialout 
- sudo usermod -aG dialout username
